<h1>Tweet Show Page</h1>

<h2>Content</h2>

<p><%=@tweet.content%></p>

<p>make sure to include edit link on show page</p>
<a href="/tweets/<%=@tweet.id%>/edit">Edit Tweet</a>


<p>add a form to delete the tweet here as well - submit via post</p>
<form action="/tweets/<%=@tweet.id%>/delete" method="post">
  <input type="hidden" id="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
  <input type="submit" name="Delete" value="Delete Tweet">
</form>
